{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"55aa40f1a9","title":"视察天津时的谈话（汇集）","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"dd9e5178f2","index":0,"year":1958,"month":8,"day":13,"articleId":"55aa40f1a9"}],"tags":[{"id":"314ad57c4d","name":"对话","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"994fc035d4","name":"工业战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"id":"e759231f2d","name":"农业战线","type":"主题/事件"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji40","name":"毛泽东全集第40卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/40-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji40":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"416d01518f","type":"title","text":"视察天津时的谈话（汇集）","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"55aa40f1a9"},{"id":"6a2acaaead","type":"paragraph","text":"对建立地方独立工业体系的指示","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"55aa40f1a9"},{"id":"1bd1f43c69","type":"paragraph","text":"地方应该想办法建立独立的工业体系。首先是协作区，然后是许多省，只要有条件，都应建立比较独立的，但是情况不同的工业体系。你们怎么样","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"55aa40f1a9"},{"id":"91542146d4","type":"paragraph","text":"视察天津大学时的指示","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"55aa40f1a9"},{"id":"502e69c8e8","type":"paragraph","text":"一个粮食，一个钢铁，有了这两个东西就什么都好办了。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"55aa40f1a9"},{"id":"74cee70c95","type":"paragraph","text":"（天津大学张国落校长向毛泽东汇报学校情况说，这个学校已有98%的学生参加了勤工检学。今年下学期还准备搞几个班半工半读。）","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"55aa40f1a9"},{"id":"2029451fc1","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东：这样很好，本来光读书本上的，没有亲自去做，有的连看也没有看过，用的时候，就做不出产品来。一搞勤工俭学、半工半读，这样有了学问，也就是劳动者了。河南省长葛县有的中学勤工俭学搞得好，学生进步快，升学的多。有的中学没有搞勤工俭学，就不好，没有学进去，把脑筋学环了。不仅学生要搞勤工俭学，教师也要搞。机关干部也要办点附属工厂，不然光讲空的，脱离实际。","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"55aa40f1a9"},{"id":"d83a3b6959","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东：（问王元之）大津中学有没有搞勤工检学","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"55aa40f1a9"},{"id":"20ecf0e72b","type":"paragraph","text":"王元之：天津近百所中学，都已搞起勤工俭学来了，六十多所中学还建立了工厂或生产车间。","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"55aa40f1a9"},{"id":"64bed59276","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东：好啊！学校是工厂，工厂也是学校，农业合作社也是学校，要好好办。","index":9,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"55aa40f1a9"},{"id":"9b436e140a","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东：以后要学校办工厂，工厂办学校。老师也要参加劳动，不能光动嘴，不动手。","index":10,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"55aa40f1a9"},{"id":"ddd13b9b4e","type":"paragraph","text":"（毛泽东对天津大学在短时期内办起许多工厂很感兴趣。）","index":11,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"55aa40f1a9"},{"id":"03fffb2755","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东：有些先生也得进步，形势逼着他们进步，他们动动手就行了。五十岁以上的教师可以不动手了，青年的、中年的都要动手。搞科学研究的人，也应该动动手，不然一辈子不动手也不好。","index":12,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"55aa40f1a9"},{"id":"1f65704d10","type":"paragraph","text":"张国灌：现在同学们搞技术革命的劲头很大。有的为了向国庆献礼，登夜突击，说服他们也说服不了。","index":13,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"55aa40f1a9"},{"id":"86e963472a","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东：连夜搞是否把人搞瘦了呢？还是注意有节奏地生产有节奏地休息和劳动。","index":14,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"55aa40f1a9"},{"id":"3d29f50c42","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东还指示","index":15,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"55aa40f1a9"},{"id":"5bea0366d4","type":"paragraph","text":"高等学校应抓住三个东西","index":16,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"55aa40f1a9"},{"id":"157c54acb8","type":"paragraph","text":"一是党委领导；","index":17,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"55aa40f1a9"},{"id":"47b43b29de","type":"paragraph","text":"二是群众路线；","index":18,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"55aa40f1a9"},{"id":"d551b56f34","type":"paragraph","text":"三是教育与生产劳动相结合。","index":19,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"55aa40f1a9"}],"page":{"id":"f3433f132e","publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"55aa40f1a9","start":23,"end":24}}}},"__N_SSG":true}